This program computes the windowed cross correlation
It was originally developed for the 
Department of Psychology, Copenhagen University.

It will install the command-line program "wcc".
To get help type wcc --help.
To get help on installation, look at the INSTALL file.

If you need a more permissive license,
or anything else to use this, please open an issue.

Also feel free to comment on 
ease of use, functionality, code style or anything else
that comes to your mind!
